The perfect holiday themed Cuervo Tradicional cocktails are here! These 3 drinks are sure to be a hit at any gathering this season! Make your own with the ingredients and steps below ‚¨áÔ∏è 

üçí Cranberry Spritz
Ingredients:
1 1/2 oz blanco tequila‚Ä¢ 1 oz cranberry juice ‚Ä¢ 1/2 oz lime juice ‚Ä¢ 3 oz sparkling water
Steps:
Add tequila, cranberry juice, and lime juice to a glass.
Add ice.
Pour in sparkling water.
Stir gently.
Garnish if you want (lime wheel, cranberries).

üçé Apple Pie Margarita
Ingredients:
2 oz a√±ejo tequila ‚Ä¢ 3 oz apple cider ‚Ä¢ 1/2 oz lemon juice ‚Ä¢ 1/2 oz brown sugar syrup ‚Ä¢
pinch pumpkin spice ‚Ä¢ apple slices + cinnamon stick
Steps:
Add tequila, apple cider, lemon juice, syrup, and pumpkin spice to a shaker.
Add ice and shake well.
Strain into a glass with fresh ice.
Garnish with apple slices and a cinnamon stick.

üíö Pistachio Espresso Martini
Ingredients:
2 oz blanco tequila ‚Ä¢ 1 oz pistachio liqueur ‚Ä¢ 1 oz espresso/cold brew concentrate ‚Ä¢ 1/2 oz 
brown sugar syrup ‚Ä¢ ice ‚Ä¢ crushed pistachios (rim)
Steps:
Rim the glass with syrup and dip in crushed pistachios.
Add tequila, pistachio liqueur, espresso, and syrup to a shaker.
Fill with ice.
Shake hard until frothy and cold.
Strain into your rimmed glass.

Margs taste so much better when our Cuervo Collective makes them ü§©üé∂ Keeping summer vibes going with the perfect sweet and spicy @josecuervotequila margarita üå∂Ô∏èüçç Recipe below!! @dinabn

Ingredients: 
2oz Cuervo Trad Blanco 
.25oz Fresh Lime Juice
.75oz  Fresh Pineapple Juice
.25oz Spicy Agave Nectar
1.5oz Grapefruit Lime Tepache 

Instructions: 
1. In a Shaker Tin, combine Cuervo, Fresh Lime Juice, Fresh Pineapple Juice, and Spicy Agave Nectar. Add ice and shake vigorously for 15 seconds.
2. Strain into a rocks glass over fresh ice. Top with 1.5oz of Grapefruit Lime Tepache. Quick stir to incorporate. 
3. Garnish with a Dehydrated Pineapple Wheel and a Tamarindo Candy Straw.
